    {
      "role": "user",
      "content": "That's a really solid starting point for them. I want to make sure they understand why it's so important, though. Some people argue that it's basically just a way for judges to make up new rights that aren't actually in the Constitution. How should I address that critique in the lesson so it doesn't undermine the importance of the doctrine?",
      "source": "evaluator"
    },
